             was indicted for <rs id="t17730707-18-off107" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17730707-18-off107" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17730707-18-off107" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               stealing two pair of men's leather shoes, value 8 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17730707-18-victim269" type="victimName">
                           Michael
                            Waring
                        <interp inst="t17730707-18-victim269" type="surname" value="Waring"></interp>
